Feature: Validate product page user  based
Scenario: Validate whether user can purchase product in limited count 

Given open browser as <BROWSER>
When Enter url as <URL>
When Enter user name as <USERNAME>
And Enter password as <PASSWORD>
When click login button
Then verify login success
When click framework form
And click simple form
Then validate user can place order upto 5 times as <PRODUCT> <MOBILE> <EMAIL> <PRODCAT> <QTY> <PURCHASER>
|product a |1111   |maila@mail.com|electrical|1   |purchaser a|
|product b |2222   |mailb@mail.com|electrical|1   |purchaser b|
|product c |3333   |mailc@mail.com|electrical|1   |purchaser c|
|product d |4444   |maild@mail.com|electrical|1   |purchaser d|
|product e |5555   |maile@mail.com|electrical|1   |purchaser e|

Then logout the user




Examples:
|BROWSER |URL |USERNAME |PASSWORD |PRODUCT   |MOBILE |EMAIL         |PRODCAT   |QTY |PURCHASER  |
